WEBVTT

1
00:00:51.720 --> 00:00:52.787
Kitana...

2
00:00:52.920 --> 00:00:54.522
I have something for you.

3
00:00:55.255 --> 00:00:56.857
It will protect you.

4
00:00:58.158 --> 00:01:00.127
It's beautiful. Father.

5
00:01:01.929 --> 00:01:03.832
This was a gift
from Lord Raiden.

6
00:01:03.964 --> 00:01:05.367
The God of Thunder.

7
00:01:06.468 --> 00:01:08.902
If anything
were to happen to me.

8
00:01:09.036 --> 00:01:11.105
he's always listening.

9
00:01:18.145 --> 00:01:20.948
Shao Kahn
is arriving. Your Majesty.

10
00:01:21.081 --> 00:01:23.984
What happens if you lose?

11
00:01:24.118 --> 00:01:25.285
Don't worry
about that.

12
00:01:25.420 --> 00:01:27.187
But what if he's too strong?

13
00:01:27.322 --> 00:01:29.791
Strength is not a closed fist.

14
00:01:29.923 --> 00:01:31.225
Strength is here.

15
00:01:32.360 --> 00:01:33.461
and here.

16
00:01:36.598 --> 00:01:38.666
Be strong. Kitana.

17
00:01:44.972 --> 00:01:49.910
Jerrod. our king!
Jerrod. our king!

18
00:02:04.459 --> 00:02:07.429
<i>Shao Kahn.</i>
<i>Emperor of Outworld.</i>

19
00:02:07.562 --> 00:02:11.366
<i>sought to unite the various</i>
<i>realms under one rule.</i>

20
00:02:11.499 --> 00:02:13.601
<i>His.</i>

21
00:02:13.735 --> 00:02:17.405
<i>But the Elder Gods had put</i>
<i>certain precautions in place.</i>

22
00:02:19.841 --> 00:02:23.378
<i>Our fates would not be settled</i>
<i>by the size of our armies.</i>

23
00:02:25.447 --> 00:02:29.116
<i>They would be decided</i>
<i>by combat.</i>

24
00:02:30.284 --> 00:02:32.387
<i>The rules were simple.</i>

25
00:02:32.520 --> 00:02:35.690
<i>If one realm could win</i>
<i>10 tournaments in a row.</i>

26
00:02:35.824 --> 00:02:38.927
<i>it would be given</i>
<i>dominion over the other.</i>

27
00:02:39.059 --> 00:02:43.030
<i>Outworld would be allowed</i>
<i>to pillage Edenia's resources.</i>

28
00:02:44.164 --> 00:02:46.133
<i>Enslave our people.</i>

29
00:02:49.838 --> 00:02:54.476
<i>This was the final tournament.</i>
<i>Our last chance.</i>

30
00:02:54.609 --> 00:02:57.679
<i>All of our greatest warriors</i>
<i>had already fallen.</i>

31
00:02:59.213 --> 00:03:01.483
<i>Only one fighter remained.</i>

32
00:03:01.616 --> 00:03:03.116
<i>My father.</i>

33
00:03:04.319 --> 00:03:07.589
<i>King Jerrod of Edenia.</i>

34
00:03:07.722 --> 00:03:11.024
<i>But he faced Outworld's</i>
<i>greatest warrior.</i>

35
00:03:13.060 --> 00:03:15.497
<i>Shao Kahn himself.</i>

36
00:03:25.540 --> 00:03:29.210
They will never bow to you.

37
00:03:29.677 --> 00:03:31.612
We shall see.

38
00:04:28.168 --> 00:04:29.304
Never!

39
00:05:24.759 --> 00:05:27.061
Kitana.
close your eyes.

40
00:05:27.194 --> 00:05:28.663
Close your eyes right now.

41
00:05:42.944 --> 00:05:46.047
No!

42
00:05:46.179 --> 00:05:47.682
No!

43
00:05:49.823 --> 00:05:52.167
No!

44
00:06:23.818 --> 00:06:27.121
Edenia
now belongs to me.

45
00:07:05.273 --> 00:07:08.376
Kneel.
Or you'll die.

46
00:08:15.830 --> 00:08:18.566
Your father shouldn't have
brought you here.

47
00:08:29.890 --> 00:08:32.893
Kitana.
you're my daughter now.

48
00:08:47.014 --> 00:08:48.015
Kitana!

49
00:09:24.833 --> 00:09:25.700
Yield.

50
00:09:45.353 --> 00:09:47.522
You cannot be serious.

51
00:09:47.655 --> 00:09:50.492
You're the one who taught me.
everything's a weapon.

52
00:09:58.600 --> 00:09:59.968
You yield.

53
00:10:14.349 --> 00:10:15.750
What do you have there?

54
00:10:16.150 --> 00:10:17.651
It's nothing.

55
00:10:19.133 --> 00:10:20.234
Jade.

56
00:10:22.525 --> 00:10:23.960
It was 20 years ago today

57
00:10:23.985 --> 00:10:26.320
the Emperor named me
as your bodyguard.

58
00:10:27.328 --> 00:10:29.630
I know what Shao Kahn
took from you.

59
00:10:29.913 --> 00:10:32.015
And if you had been vicious
or cruel to me.

60
00:10:32.040 --> 00:10:33.207
no one would have blamed you.

61
00:10:33.254 --> 00:10:36.123
but you treated me
like family.

62
00:10:36.705 --> 00:10:37.906
Like a sister.

63
00:10:39.875 --> 00:10:42.043
You are my sister.

64
00:10:42.177 --> 00:10:44.146
In every way that matters.

65
00:10:47.361 --> 00:10:51.331
Um. I got you something.
For the tournament.

66
00:10:55.724 --> 00:10:57.159
I was told
that a proper princess

67
00:10:57.292 --> 00:11:00.428
is supposed to sit around
on pillows fanning herself.

68
00:11:01.763 --> 00:11:03.098
Then I thought

69
00:11:03.638 --> 00:11:06.841
you are not exactly
the pillow type.

70
00:11:11.179 --> 00:11:12.580
These are amazing.

71
00:11:25.487 --> 00:11:27.590
Hello. Mother.

72
00:11:27.722 --> 00:11:31.226
I was beginning
to think you were avoiding me.

73
00:11:31.552 --> 00:11:34.355
I've been busy.
Training for the tournament.

74
00:11:35.797 --> 00:11:37.766
Good.
Because I have petitioned

75
00:11:37.899 --> 00:11:40.368
the Elder Gods
for the tournament to begin.

76
00:11:40.503 --> 00:11:43.673
Let Raiden scrounge
for his little champions.

77
00:11:43.805 --> 00:11:46.441
They will simply
be the first to die

78
00:11:46.708 --> 00:11:48.575
and Earthrealm will be mine.

79
00:11:54.916 --> 00:11:56.218
Why is he here?

80
00:11:56.351 --> 00:11:58.920
I have a task
for Shang Tsung.

81
00:11:59.988 --> 00:12:02.724
I hope you bring
good news. Sorcerer.

82
00:12:02.857 --> 00:12:05.561
My spies have located
the relic.

83
00:12:05.695 --> 00:12:07.395
It was last seen
in Raiden's temple

84
00:12:07.530 --> 00:12:11.032
where it was stolen
by the mercenary. Kano.

85
00:12:11.166 --> 00:12:13.569
We seek the Amulet of Shinnok.

86
00:12:13.703 --> 00:12:16.639
It is said the Amulet
can heal any wound.

87
00:12:16.771 --> 00:12:18.873
Transform a man into a god.

88
00:12:19.007 --> 00:12:20.576
To charge the amulet
would require

89
00:12:20.710 --> 00:12:22.744
an impossible amount of power.

90
00:12:22.877 --> 00:12:25.814
We would need to capture
a star from the heavens.

91
00:12:25.947 --> 00:12:28.584
A star...

92
00:12:28.718 --> 00:12:31.119
...or a god.

93
00:12:31.253 --> 00:12:33.255
Outworld has issued
their challenge

94
00:12:33.388 --> 00:12:35.056
and the Elder Gods
have spoken.

95
00:12:35.190 --> 00:12:39.629
When the sand is gone.
the first round will begin.

96
00:12:39.761 --> 00:12:42.330
Mortal Kombat is upon us

97
00:12:42.464 --> 00:12:46.001
and yet we are still short
one champion.

98
00:13:06.288 --> 00:13:08.691
♪ <i>Here I am</i> ♪

99
00:13:08.823 --> 00:13:14.262
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

100
00:13:40.088 --> 00:13:42.991
It's showtime.

101
00:13:47.697 --> 00:13:49.864
♪ <i>Are you ready. baby?</i> ♪

102
00:13:58.940 --> 00:14:00.241
♪ <i>Here I am</i> ♪

103
00:14:01.544 --> 00:14:04.913
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

104
00:14:06.915 --> 00:14:09.150
♪ <i>Here I am</i> ♪

105
00:14:09.284 --> 00:14:11.419
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

106
00:14:21.564 --> 00:14:23.932
You should have
brought more guys.

107
00:14:24.065 --> 00:14:25.568
♪ <i>The sun comes out</i> ♪

108
00:14:25.701 --> 00:14:29.605
♪ <i>Last night was shaking</i>
<i>And pretty loud</i> ♪

109
00:14:31.567 --> 00:14:33.435
♪ <i>It scratches my skin</i> ♪

110
00:14:33.509 --> 00:14:37.513
♪ <i>So what is wrong</i>
<i>With another sin?</i> ♪

111
00:14:43.485 --> 00:14:45.588
♪ <i>Yeah. yeah. yeah. yeah</i> ♪

112
00:14:45.721 --> 00:14:47.989
♪ <i>Here I am</i> ♪

113
00:14:48.123 --> 00:14:50.760
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

114
00:14:50.892 --> 00:14:53.395
♪ <i>Come on. come on</i>
<i>Come on. come on</i> ♪

115
00:14:56.224 --> 00:14:57.725
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

116
00:14:58.065 --> 00:15:00.001
Man. Johnny Cage
got old as fuck.

117
00:15:05.206 --> 00:15:06.876
<i>Attention. fans.</i>

118
00:15:07.008 --> 00:15:09.010
<i>don't miss your chance to meet</i>
<i>your favorite influencers</i>

119
00:15:09.144 --> 00:15:11.946
<i>and YouTube stars</i>
<i>in Autograph Alley.</i>

120
00:15:12.080 --> 00:15:13.816
All right.
everyone. get in close.

121
00:15:13.948 --> 00:15:14.916
Black Orchid!

122
00:15:24.894 --> 00:15:26.227
<i>It's showtime.</i>

123
00:15:42.043 --> 00:15:43.779
Johnny Cage.

124
00:15:43.913 --> 00:15:46.649
Hey. guys. I'm off the clock.

125
00:15:46.782 --> 00:15:50.853
Mr. Cage. you have been chosen
for Mortal Kombat.

126
00:15:51.019 --> 00:15:52.588
Mortal Kombat. huh?

127
00:15:52.721 --> 00:15:54.690
What's that?
Some kind of fan film?

128
00:15:54.824 --> 00:15:56.257
It's a fighting tournament.

129
00:15:56.391 --> 00:15:59.394
Yeah. not really
my thing anymore.

130
00:16:01.262 --> 00:16:02.765
Unless it's a paying gig?

131
00:16:02.898 --> 00:16:05.568
More like a "fate
of the entire human race" gig.

132
00:16:05.701 --> 00:16:08.571
Tell me you're
not some crazy fans.

133
00:16:08.704 --> 00:16:10.271
Definitely not fans.

134
00:16:10.405 --> 00:16:12.273
All right. All right.
You don't
have to say "definitely."

135
00:16:12.407 --> 00:16:13.642
You have been chosen

136
00:16:13.776 --> 00:16:15.578
as one of the champions
of Earthrealm.

137
00:16:15.711 --> 00:16:19.180
The gods have selected you.
Mr. Cage.

138
00:16:19.314 --> 00:16:21.650
All right. I think it's time
for you guys to fuck off.

139
00:16:21.784 --> 00:16:24.219
But. hey. love the cosplay.
What's that?

140
00:16:24.352 --> 00:16:26.254
<i>Big Trouble in Little China?</i>
Fantastic film.

141
00:16:26.387 --> 00:16:27.957
Listen. I know
what it sounds like.

142
00:16:28.089 --> 00:16:29.457
but he's telling the truth.

143
00:16:29.592 --> 00:16:32.795
Very soon the champions
will be summoned to fight

144
00:16:32.928 --> 00:16:34.195
and you will be among them.

145
00:16:34.329 --> 00:16:35.631
The fate of your world

146
00:16:35.764 --> 00:16:38.266
rests on the outcome
of this tournament.

147
00:16:38.399 --> 00:16:40.936
Fantastic.
I will see you there.

148
00:16:41.069 --> 00:16:42.538
Thanks for coming. drive safe.

149
00:16:42.671 --> 00:16:44.940
and. uh. say hi to Dumbledore
for me.

150
00:16:45.073 --> 00:16:47.075
You're gonna have to show him.

151
00:17:01.256 --> 00:17:03.659
Holy shit.

152
00:17:03.792 --> 00:17:05.093
How are you doing that?

153
00:17:05.226 --> 00:17:06.729
Come with us.
Mr. Cage.

154
00:17:06.862 --> 00:17:09.798
and discover the man
you were meant to be.

155
00:17:16.271 --> 00:17:18.072
Now are you coming or what?

156
00:17:43.398 --> 00:17:46.200
Where the hell am I?

157
00:17:46.334 --> 00:17:48.236
It's okay.
You're still on Earth.

158
00:17:48.369 --> 00:17:50.104
Welcome
to Raiden's Sky Temple.

159
00:17:56.612 --> 00:17:59.548
Watch this.

160
00:17:59.682 --> 00:18:03.719
Robot arms.
That dude's got robot arms.

161
00:18:03.852 --> 00:18:05.320
We served
in the Army together.

162
00:18:05.453 --> 00:18:07.756
That's Jax Briggs.
Special Forces.

163
00:18:08.991 --> 00:18:10.325
That's Cole Young.

164
00:18:10.458 --> 00:18:13.361
His suit absorbs attacks
and makes him stronger.

165
00:18:13.494 --> 00:18:14.830
He's a descendant of Scorpion.

166
00:18:14.964 --> 00:18:17.365
One of Earthrealm's
greatest warriors.

167
00:18:18.232 --> 00:18:19.167
Oh.

168
00:18:19.300 --> 00:18:21.135
That's Liu Kang.

169
00:18:21.269 --> 00:18:23.171
He's the best fighter we got.

170
00:18:31.446 --> 00:18:33.615
- He shoots fire?
- Mm-hmm.

171
00:18:35.264 --> 00:18:38.634
I feel like that's cheating.
but okay.

172
00:18:39.220 --> 00:18:40.388
It kind of feels like bullshit

173
00:18:40.522 --> 00:18:42.223
that y'all have
these crazy powers

174
00:18:42.357 --> 00:18:45.527
and I'm just. you know.
incredibly handsome.

175
00:18:45.661 --> 00:18:47.062
It could take
months of training

176
00:18:47.195 --> 00:18:48.731
to unlock your powers.

177
00:18:48.864 --> 00:18:50.198
We don't have
that kind of time.

178
00:18:50.331 --> 00:18:51.567
Yeah.
well. whose fault is that?

179
00:18:51.700 --> 00:18:53.301
I mean.
if you knew this was coming.

180
00:18:53.434 --> 00:18:54.770
why'd you wait till the
last second to find me?

181
00:18:54.903 --> 00:18:57.506
We used to have
another champion. Kung Lao.

182
00:18:57.640 --> 00:18:59.240
Oh. great.
so I'm just the fucking sub.

183
00:18:59.374 --> 00:19:01.376
He was murdered.
By Shang Tsung.

184
00:19:01.510 --> 00:19:03.846
Wait. Murdered?

185
00:19:05.446 --> 00:19:07.816
Come on.
You can't be serious. Right?

186
00:19:07.950 --> 00:19:10.719
I mean. that's. like.
gotta be against the rules.

187
00:19:10.853 --> 00:19:13.254
You can't just go around
killing people.

188
00:19:14.455 --> 00:19:17.793
It's called Mortal Kombat
for a reason.

189
00:19:17.926 --> 00:19:21.130
Yo. Gandalf. send me back.
I wanna go back.

190
00:19:21.262 --> 00:19:23.599
-Johnny. wait.
-No. No.

191
00:19:23.732 --> 00:19:25.534
You said tournament
which implies rules.

192
00:19:25.668 --> 00:19:27.603
and a referee. and I don't
know. maybe a medic.

193
00:19:27.736 --> 00:19:29.772
Not some fucking <i>Squid Game</i>
murder party.

194
00:19:29.905 --> 00:19:32.041
Dude wants to quit.
just let him go.

195
00:19:32.173 --> 00:19:33.509
We don't need him.

196
00:19:33.642 --> 00:19:36.277
Look. you wanna step
in the octagon

197
00:19:36.411 --> 00:19:37.780
with a bunch
of happy assholes

198
00:19:37.913 --> 00:19:41.016
that don't know how to lose.
go right ahead.

199
00:19:41.150 --> 00:19:43.351
But I don't have
Transformer arms.

200
00:19:43.484 --> 00:19:46.387
or shoot lightning bolts
or fireballs.

201
00:19:46.522 --> 00:19:48.857
or do whatever the fuck it is
Flame Fingers does.

202
00:19:48.991 --> 00:19:52.326
so forgive me if I don't
sign up to get mulched.

203
00:19:55.698 --> 00:19:58.266
You are not wrong. Mr. Cage.

204
00:20:05.887 --> 00:20:07.623
Nine times.
we have been challenged.

205
00:20:07.916 --> 00:20:09.684
And nine times. we have lost.

206
00:20:09.911 --> 00:20:11.479
And now. 20 years later.

207
00:20:11.504 --> 00:20:15.091
Shao Kahn seeks to add
Earthrealm to his dominion.

208
00:20:15.491 --> 00:20:19.361
This is a war
for the fate of your world.

209
00:20:19.675 --> 00:20:22.578
Look. Cage. I get it.
We all do.

210
00:20:22.858 --> 00:20:24.660
Some stupid. fucking.
cosmic lottery

211
00:20:24.685 --> 00:20:27.855
decided that we're the ones
that get to save the world.

212
00:20:29.904 --> 00:20:31.774
Shit is terrifying.

213
00:20:32.333 --> 00:20:34.435
You wanna know
the last thing I did
before coming here?

214
00:20:34.570 --> 00:20:37.840
I said goodbye to my wife
and my little girl.

215
00:20:37.973 --> 00:20:41.275
The two most important things
in my life.

216
00:20:41.409 --> 00:20:42.477
And there's a damn good chance

217
00:20:42.611 --> 00:20:44.680
I'm never
gonna see them again.

218
00:20:45.594 --> 00:20:47.563
And I'm okay with that.

219
00:20:47.949 --> 00:20:51.287
Because I know if I die
out there. I'm dying for them.

220
00:20:52.468 --> 00:20:54.937
We lose one more time.
the Earth is gone.

221
00:20:55.356 --> 00:20:58.459
And our only chance
is to face this together.

222
00:20:58.594 --> 00:21:03.297
You. Johnny Cage.
are a part of this now.

223
00:21:11.506 --> 00:21:12.739
Fuck that.

224
00:21:13.047 --> 00:21:14.383
Johnny.
even if you walk away.

225
00:21:14.510 --> 00:21:16.145
the Elder Gods
can still summon you to fight.

226
00:21:16.278 --> 00:21:17.612
Not if they can't find me.

227
00:21:17.665 --> 00:21:19.013
So what are you gonna do. huh?

228
00:21:19.345 --> 00:21:20.483
You just going to go hide?

229
00:21:20.616 --> 00:21:22.685
No. first I'm gonna drink
every beer on the planet.

230
00:21:22.818 --> 00:21:24.186
then I'm going to hide.

231
00:21:24.320 --> 00:21:25.788
Because this shit's
got nothing to do with me.

232
00:21:26.248 --> 00:21:27.757
I'm not some great warrior.

233
00:21:27.889 --> 00:21:29.449
I'm not some champion.

234
00:21:29.669 --> 00:21:31.627
Okay? I'm an actor.

235
00:21:31.761 --> 00:21:32.750
Hmm.

236
00:21:33.863 --> 00:21:35.131
And before that.
you were the guy

237
00:21:35.264 --> 00:21:37.633
with five black belts
and a world title.

238
00:21:39.468 --> 00:21:43.239
Yeah. I saw
some of those old fights.

239
00:21:43.372 --> 00:21:46.442
Man. you could have been
one of the best.

240
00:21:46.575 --> 00:21:49.345
But I wasn't.
And that was a long time ago.

241
00:21:49.478 --> 00:21:52.536
That guy you want
is dead and buried.

242
00:21:53.249 --> 00:21:55.584
Or maybe he's still in there
trying to get out.

243
00:22:15.970 --> 00:22:17.173
Hey. listen...

244
00:22:19.208 --> 00:22:21.377
I'm like 90% sure
I had an aneurysm

245
00:22:21.402 --> 00:22:24.113
and this is some kind of
fucked up coma dream.

246
00:22:25.781 --> 00:22:28.117
but on the off chance
this shit is real.

247
00:22:29.552 --> 00:22:31.720
best of luck with the whole
saving the world thing.

248
00:22:46.968 --> 00:22:50.206
You should know
that when you died.

249
00:22:50.339 --> 00:22:55.043
it was not your so-called
friends who brought you back.

250
00:22:56.010 --> 00:22:58.180
It was not Lord Raiden.

251
00:22:58.948 --> 00:23:01.317
the Great Pretender.

252
00:23:02.818 --> 00:23:05.086
It was Shao Kahn.

253
00:23:06.155 --> 00:23:08.657
Rise now.

254
00:23:08.791 --> 00:23:12.228
as a champion of Outworld.

255
00:23:19.039 --> 00:23:22.610
Sire.
we retrieved the package.

256
00:23:24.480 --> 00:23:26.015
Quan Chi!

257
00:23:26.442 --> 00:23:29.043
I am told you sent your
followers to Earthrealm.

258
00:23:29.178 --> 00:23:30.479
What were they doing there?

259
00:23:30.517 --> 00:23:34.015
Simply retrieving
some lost property. my lady.

260
00:23:34.149 --> 00:23:36.252
By order of your father.

261
00:23:38.453 --> 00:23:39.820
What is that?

262
00:23:44.226 --> 00:23:46.195
I believe it's called...

263
00:23:46.894 --> 00:23:48.263
a "Kano."

264
00:23:53.168 --> 00:23:55.204
One Sling Dog. please.

265
00:24:00.223 --> 00:24:02.325
You're Johnny Cage.

266
00:24:03.012 --> 00:24:04.547
That's what the tab says.

267
00:24:04.680 --> 00:24:06.282
Holy shit.

268
00:24:06.415 --> 00:24:10.519
I freaking loved <i>Citizen Cage</i>
when I was a kid.

269
00:24:11.939 --> 00:24:13.822
Thanks. man. I appreciate it.

270
00:24:15.624 --> 00:24:17.535
Dude. you know
what they should do?

271
00:24:18.427 --> 00:24:21.062
They should
do another <i>Citizen Cage.</i>

272
00:24:21.087 --> 00:24:22.823
Like a reboot.

273
00:24:23.064 --> 00:24:25.019
Come on. man.
Give me a break.

274
00:24:25.614 --> 00:24:27.716
-Nobody wants that.
-What?

275
00:24:27.836 --> 00:24:29.371
You think the world
is crying out

276
00:24:29.505 --> 00:24:33.242
for a Johnny Cage comeback?
Huh?

277
00:24:33.375 --> 00:24:35.711
No. They want gritty.
they want grounded.

278
00:24:35.844 --> 00:24:37.246
they want Keanu Reeves

279
00:24:37.379 --> 00:24:39.080
murdering a thousand
fucking dudes with a pencil.

280
00:24:39.105 --> 00:24:41.074
That's what people wanna see.

281
00:24:42.624 --> 00:24:46.794
Not some dinosaur
doing a bunch of karate poses.

282
00:24:48.089 --> 00:24:50.125
That shit went out
in the '90's.

283
00:24:53.690 --> 00:24:55.425
I thought it was pretty cool.

284
00:25:40.776 --> 00:25:43.078
Where's my fucking eye?

285
00:25:46.649 --> 00:25:47.716
Blondie.

286
00:25:49.051 --> 00:25:50.886
The tournament
has begun.

287
00:25:51.020 --> 00:25:53.088
Today you fight
for Earthrealm.

288
00:25:53.222 --> 00:25:55.624
For the lives of everyone
you have ever known.

289
00:25:55.758 --> 00:25:59.195
If you fail.
the Earth fails with you.

290
00:25:59.328 --> 00:26:02.965
Two of our champions will
be chosen to compete today.

291
00:26:03.098 --> 00:26:04.341
The winners will advance

292
00:26:04.366 --> 00:26:06.235
to the next stage
of the tournament.

293
00:26:06.724 --> 00:26:09.405
The losers will be eliminated.

294
00:26:09.538 --> 00:26:10.272
To the death.

295
00:26:10.406 --> 00:26:12.341
That is up to the winner.

296
00:26:13.242 --> 00:26:14.810
Maybe don't lose.

297
00:26:20.483 --> 00:26:22.284
Well. looks like
it's my lucky day.

298
00:26:22.418 --> 00:26:24.753
Blade. you got this.

299
00:26:30.593 --> 00:26:32.595
I thought you said
two of us were fighting.

300
00:26:37.266 --> 00:26:41.070
<i>It's Johnny Cage</i>
<i>with a brutal hit. He's down.</i>

301
00:26:41.831 --> 00:26:42.813
<i>It's official.</i>

302
00:26:42.838 --> 00:26:45.583
<i>Johnny Cage just became</i>
<i>the youngest minor</i>

303
00:26:45.608 --> 00:26:47.209
<i>to ever win this tournament.</i>

304
00:26:47.343 --> 00:26:50.179
<i>This young man</i>
<i>is destined for greatness.</i>

305
00:26:53.362 --> 00:26:56.131
You seem
a little down. Johnny.

306
00:26:56.452 --> 00:26:58.554
You're normally
a little more animated.

307
00:27:05.160 --> 00:27:06.762
<i>Uno mas.</i> thanks. Ed.

308
00:27:26.882 --> 00:27:29.051
Oh. shit.

309
00:27:33.856 --> 00:27:35.124
I don't know
what you're on about.

310
00:27:35.257 --> 00:27:36.692
The amulet of what now?

311
00:27:36.825 --> 00:27:38.460
Shinnok. Pay attention!

312
00:27:38.594 --> 00:27:40.262
Don't look at me
with that tone of voice.

313
00:27:40.396 --> 00:27:41.764
you big bleached dildo.

314
00:27:41.897 --> 00:27:44.521
I've just been dead.
And my fucking eye's AWOL.

315
00:27:44.546 --> 00:27:47.736
Stop your incessant whinging.
We can build you another.

316
00:27:47.870 --> 00:27:49.672
Why is he not a Revenant
like the rest of them?

317
00:27:49.805 --> 00:27:52.374
He was not worth
the time or the effort.

318
00:27:52.508 --> 00:27:55.144
This one barely has a soul
left to corrupt.

319
00:27:55.277 --> 00:27:57.379
Ha! You hear that?
A fucking loophole.

320
00:27:57.513 --> 00:27:58.949
Go. you good thing.

321
00:27:59.081 --> 00:28:02.217
Where is the amulet you took
from Raiden's temple?

322
00:28:02.351 --> 00:28:03.686
I don't know.
probably in my pocket

323
00:28:03.819 --> 00:28:05.487
where I keep
all the shit I steal.

324
00:28:07.057 --> 00:28:08.791
Oh. right-oh.

325
00:28:10.927 --> 00:28:15.031
Here we go. How about...

326
00:28:15.164 --> 00:28:17.934
Nah. different temple.
Well. hold on.

327
00:28:18.068 --> 00:28:19.435
This could be...

328
00:28:19.568 --> 00:28:21.637
Yeah.
Should call her.

329
00:28:22.404 --> 00:28:25.608
Ah! Here we are. Yahtzee.

330
00:28:25.694 --> 00:28:26.630
Oi!

331
00:28:27.209 --> 00:28:28.243
We could have left him dead.

332
00:28:28.377 --> 00:28:30.145
Hey! First off. fuck off.

333
00:28:30.279 --> 00:28:32.281
And you.
where are you going with that?

334
00:28:33.282 --> 00:28:34.883
I will take it to my father.

335
00:28:36.251 --> 00:28:37.486
Unfortunately. Princess.

336
00:28:37.620 --> 00:28:40.122
it appears
you are needed elsewhere.

337
00:28:42.358 --> 00:28:44.027
Oi. you creepy fucking mime.

338
00:28:44.159 --> 00:28:46.295
I stole that fair and square.

339
00:28:47.296 --> 00:28:48.597
Good luck.

340
00:29:09.418 --> 00:29:12.088
Each flame
represents a fighter.

341
00:29:12.254 --> 00:29:13.422
The tournament ends
when one side

342
00:29:13.555 --> 00:29:15.357
has no champions left.

343
00:29:16.225 --> 00:29:17.760
Hey. How's it going. babe?

344
00:29:19.716 --> 00:29:22.886
Listen. I'm warning you.

345
00:29:23.232 --> 00:29:26.268
I got a Saturn Award for
best fight in a feature film.

346
00:29:26.402 --> 00:29:27.971
so don't mess with me.

347
00:29:31.774 --> 00:29:34.054
Whoa! Whoa. Easy. all right.

348
00:29:34.110 --> 00:29:36.512
Let's just take a timeout here
and talk about it.

349
00:29:36.645 --> 00:29:39.648
Okay? I really don't feel
comfortable hitting a girl.

350
00:29:40.976 --> 00:29:43.345
Don't worry. you won't.

351
00:29:54.863 --> 00:29:56.899
Whoa! Come on. Easy.
Let's just talk about this.

352
00:30:19.822 --> 00:30:21.256
Why are you so fucking mean?

353
00:32:13.344 --> 00:32:14.777
Finish him!

354
00:32:28.884 --> 00:32:30.219
Hmm.

355
00:32:54.449 --> 00:32:57.152
It appears your side
is already down a man.

356
00:32:57.847 --> 00:32:59.115
Tragic.

357
00:33:02.128 --> 00:33:03.362
And who are you?

358
00:33:03.593 --> 00:33:06.261
Sindel. High Queen of Edenia.

359
00:33:06.388 --> 00:33:08.959
Consort to the great
Shao Kahn.

360
00:33:09.091 --> 00:33:10.993
They send their queen
to fight?

361
00:33:11.126 --> 00:33:14.497
No. We send our best to fight.

362
00:33:14.898 --> 00:33:15.577
Oh.

363
00:33:16.103 --> 00:33:18.514
No offense. babe. but you look
really fucking dead.

364
00:33:18.635 --> 00:33:20.971
I was freed
from my mortal bonds.

365
00:33:21.103 --> 00:33:22.238
Shao Kahn showed me

366
00:33:22.371 --> 00:33:23.940
the pleasures
of a life eternal.

367
00:33:28.512 --> 00:33:30.580
Perhaps I'll do the same
for you.

368
00:33:40.389 --> 00:33:42.692
What a pretty trick.

369
00:33:42.826 --> 00:33:44.539
Would you like to see mine?

370
00:33:45.126 --> 00:33:47.096
No. actually I'm good.

371
00:34:10.052 --> 00:34:13.436
Fuck you!
You stupid bitch!

372
00:35:18.952 --> 00:35:21.524
It appears
our sides are now even.

373
00:35:26.596 --> 00:35:28.464
What'd I miss?

374
00:35:28.598 --> 00:35:31.133
Fuck yeah! Look who's back.

375
00:35:32.355 --> 00:35:34.557
Well? How bad was it?

376
00:35:34.938 --> 00:35:38.307
Zombie queen.
Pit of spikes. Yeah.

377
00:35:38.440 --> 00:35:40.110
-So pretty goddamn bad.
-Ow.

378
00:35:41.878 --> 00:35:43.345
-You okay?
-Yeah.

379
00:35:47.310 --> 00:35:48.378
What happened?

380
00:35:48.685 --> 00:35:51.019
You were eliminated
from the tournament.

381
00:35:52.221 --> 00:35:53.227
You lost.

382
00:35:53.373 --> 00:35:56.512
You are lucky. she was
charitable and let you live.

383
00:36:03.859 --> 00:36:05.395
Oi! Pennywise.

384
00:36:05.835 --> 00:36:08.104
I've been looking all over
this shithole for you.

385
00:36:08.237 --> 00:36:09.639
You promised me a new eye.

386
00:36:09.773 --> 00:36:11.775
And it better be one
that shoots lasers.

387
00:36:11.800 --> 00:36:15.058
- I have other priorities.
- Like fucking what?

388
00:36:15.225 --> 00:36:16.478
If it's putting on
more eyeliner.

389
00:36:16.532 --> 00:36:18.033
trust me. you're good.

390
00:36:18.247 --> 00:36:19.549
All right? Come on. mate.

391
00:36:19.574 --> 00:36:21.742
I am bumping into shit
left. right. and center.

392
00:36:21.985 --> 00:36:23.887
I mean. my peripheral vision
is fucked.

393
00:36:24.020 --> 00:36:25.522
Proper fucked. mate.

394
00:36:25.655 --> 00:36:27.724
So come on.
Chop-chop. Let's get to it.

395
00:36:29.118 --> 00:36:30.794
Well. you don't have
to do it right now.

396
00:36:30.927 --> 00:36:33.630
I mean. you need to.
you know. take a measurement.

397
00:36:33.763 --> 00:36:37.366
Check the color or wash
your grubby little hands.

398
00:36:39.902 --> 00:36:41.338
All right. let's have a look.

399
00:36:41.450 --> 00:36:44.387
Don't fucking roll it on
the fucking ground. you grub!

400
00:36:45.689 --> 00:36:47.856
Oi. the amulet.

401
00:36:48.377 --> 00:36:50.780
I want that back.
And don't fucking roll it.

402
00:36:50.914 --> 00:36:53.650
You got your eye.
Now leave me alone.

403
00:36:53.729 --> 00:36:56.297
The amulet
does not belong to you.

404
00:36:56.404 --> 00:36:58.392
Its powers are well beyond

405
00:36:58.420 --> 00:37:00.523
your meager understanding.

406
00:37:00.657 --> 00:37:01.891
Idiot.

407
00:37:02.025 --> 00:37:03.760
All right. Let's take
this baby for a test drive.

408
00:37:04.661 --> 00:37:07.463
All right.

409
00:37:07.597 --> 00:37:12.602
One. two. three.
Oh! Fuck! Snug.

410
00:37:15.471 --> 00:37:16.973
Wow.

411
00:37:17.107 --> 00:37:19.509
Holy shit. is that HD?
That's pretty good.

412
00:37:19.642 --> 00:37:22.377
How many eyes you made?
Can you do me other one?

413
00:37:35.097 --> 00:37:37.200
You seem troubled. Mr. Cage.

414
00:37:38.928 --> 00:37:41.029
Yeah. Well. 'cause of me

415
00:37:41.054 --> 00:37:43.691
Earth's odds
just got 20% worse.

416
00:37:44.200 --> 00:37:46.503
I had a chance to actually
do something worth a damn

417
00:37:46.549 --> 00:37:47.984
and I screwed it all up.

418
00:37:48.204 --> 00:37:52.675
So. yeah. I'd say "troubled"
just about sums it up.

419
00:38:00.146 --> 00:38:03.820
What are those? Pills?

420
00:38:03.987 --> 00:38:04.987
Huh?

421
00:38:05.755 --> 00:38:07.290
Are they magic fighting pills?

422
00:38:08.125 --> 00:38:10.260
Is that how
you get your powers?

423
00:38:19.970 --> 00:38:21.203
Bird seed.

424
00:38:22.539 --> 00:38:26.843
Oh. Yeah. yeah. yeah.
Bird seed. Yeah.

425
00:38:26.977 --> 00:38:30.413
Well. I thought you were gonna
give me some kind of lecture.

426
00:38:30.547 --> 00:38:34.451
but. yeah. chores are good.

427
00:38:36.720 --> 00:38:38.588
You don't need a lecture.

428
00:38:38.722 --> 00:38:40.022
You need perspective.

429
00:38:41.510 --> 00:38:42.526
Perspective. huh?

430
00:38:42.659 --> 00:38:44.960
There are eight billion people
on this planet

431
00:38:45.094 --> 00:38:47.130
and yet the gods chose you.

432
00:38:47.264 --> 00:38:49.199
Perhaps they saw
your true potential

433
00:38:49.332 --> 00:38:51.802
as a champion of Earthrealm.

434
00:38:51.934 --> 00:38:53.503
Maybe they made a mistake.

435
00:38:53.637 --> 00:38:54.805
Maybe.

436
00:38:54.937 --> 00:38:58.208
If I see the Elder Gods.
I'll be sure to tell them.

437
00:39:02.679 --> 00:39:05.345
Well. I'm glad
you find this all so amusing.

438
00:39:06.383 --> 00:39:10.187
Hey. great pep talk.
by the way. Just nailed it.

439
00:39:55.672 --> 00:39:56.872
Ouch.

440
00:39:57.787 --> 00:39:59.789
You have done this before?

441
00:40:00.650 --> 00:40:02.052
I've seen it done.

442
00:40:03.959 --> 00:40:05.127
All right.

443
00:40:10.480 --> 00:40:14.184
It's okay. The Princess Kitana
has been my eyes and ears

444
00:40:14.317 --> 00:40:16.419
inside the palace
for many years now.

445
00:40:17.754 --> 00:40:19.923
We know the risk you took
coming here.

446
00:40:20.089 --> 00:40:21.324
Thank you. Kitana.

447
00:40:21.458 --> 00:40:23.660
Wait. are you telling me
I got my ass kicked

448
00:40:23.793 --> 00:40:25.060
by one of the good guys?

449
00:40:25.195 --> 00:40:27.862
I had to make it look real.
He was watching.

450
00:40:28.698 --> 00:40:30.570
They found
the Amulet of Shinnok.

451
00:40:31.142 --> 00:40:32.277
It was in the possession

452
00:40:32.302 --> 00:40:34.004
of a dead sellsword
named Kano.

453
00:40:34.137 --> 00:40:35.572
Son of a bitch.

454
00:40:35.705 --> 00:40:37.574
If the Emperor finds a way
to charge the amulet.

455
00:40:37.599 --> 00:40:39.168
he would be unstoppable.

456
00:40:39.409 --> 00:40:40.944
It would be
like fighting a god.

457
00:40:41.076 --> 00:40:43.566
Yeah. well. let's not do that.

458
00:40:44.281 --> 00:40:45.988
My friend
is in the tournament.

459
00:40:47.109 --> 00:40:49.241
Jade was raised
under Shao Kahn's army.

460
00:40:49.786 --> 00:40:54.056
Do what you must.
but do not make her suffer.

461
00:41:05.701 --> 00:41:07.837
You went to another realm?

462
00:41:10.340 --> 00:41:11.541
You followed me?

463
00:41:11.783 --> 00:41:13.985
I am trying to keep you alive.

464
00:41:14.010 --> 00:41:15.312
By spying on your friend.

465
00:41:15.337 --> 00:41:17.639
By keeping my friend
from making a mistake.

466
00:41:17.881 --> 00:41:21.351
You are conspiring
with Lord Raiden. The enemy.

467
00:41:21.484 --> 00:41:23.876
I swore an oath. Kitana.

468
00:41:24.588 --> 00:41:28.391
To serve as Shao Kahn's sword.

469
00:41:35.632 --> 00:41:37.367
The second round
of the tournament

470
00:41:37.392 --> 00:41:39.862
will consist of three matches.

471
00:41:40.102 --> 00:41:43.173
Jax. Cole. Liu Kang.

472
00:42:00.357 --> 00:42:01.858
Kung Lao.

473
00:42:02.707 --> 00:42:04.661
I have been given new life.

474
00:42:05.374 --> 00:42:06.842
My son?

475
00:42:16.039 --> 00:42:19.676
Look at that.
Still part of this tournament.

476
00:42:19.929 --> 00:42:21.431
But that's not why I'm here.

477
00:42:30.720 --> 00:42:32.589
No!

478
00:42:32.722 --> 00:42:33.823
No!

479
00:42:45.014 --> 00:42:46.482
Attack now!

480
00:43:24.768 --> 00:43:29.581
Imagine what one
could do with such power.

481
00:43:31.081 --> 00:43:35.885
Careful. Sorcerer.
that doesn't belong to you.

482
00:43:42.901 --> 00:43:45.927
The amulet must be bound
to a mortal soul.

483
00:43:46.020 --> 00:43:47.855
Once it has imprinted
on to you.

484
00:43:48.017 --> 00:43:50.320
Raiden's power will be yours.

485
00:43:50.486 --> 00:43:52.955
The amulet
will give you immortality.

486
00:44:56.787 --> 00:45:00.456
Well. this is fucking ominous.

487
00:45:07.110 --> 00:45:08.880
I'm guessing you're Jade.

488
00:45:09.012 --> 00:45:10.914
Let's get this over with.

489
00:45:16.486 --> 00:45:19.222
I am told you carry
the blood of Scorpion.

490
00:45:23.260 --> 00:45:25.395
I look forward to spilling it.

491
00:45:39.869 --> 00:45:42.205
You know you're fighting
on the wrong side. right?

492
00:45:52.522 --> 00:45:54.691
What the fuck
do you have under there?

493
00:45:55.959 --> 00:45:58.687
Shit.

494
00:46:17.748 --> 00:46:19.216
Well. hello there.

495
00:46:27.457 --> 00:46:30.260
I hope
your ancestors are watching.

496
00:47:01.726 --> 00:47:05.161
For what it is worth.
I take no joy in this.

497
00:47:07.732 --> 00:47:10.033
Then you're really going
to hate this shit.

498
00:47:15.272 --> 00:47:16.807
This is for my family.

499
00:47:17.622 --> 00:47:19.624
For my friends.

500
00:47:19.836 --> 00:47:22.372
For every moment
that brought me here.

501
00:47:22.813 --> 00:47:26.516
This is for Earth.
you son of a bitch.

502
00:48:14.639 --> 00:48:16.132
What?

503
00:48:40.624 --> 00:48:42.860
Give my regards to the dead.

504
00:48:51.241 --> 00:48:54.571
Go on. do it.

505
00:49:17.629 --> 00:49:19.162
Why?

506
00:49:19.609 --> 00:49:21.745
Your friend spared
one of our guys.

507
00:49:22.734 --> 00:49:23.867
Now we're even.

508
